room_title: Escape room "Boardwalk Blast" by Escape Garden State in New York
review: All ages enjoyed the Boardwalk escape. Grandchildren ages 4 to 16 and mom and grandma had fun too. The man who assisted was a gentleman and made the day even nicer. We will definitely return and try another escape room.

room_title: Escape room "Boardwalk Blast" by Escape Garden State in New York
review: Have done so many rooms and last night we did the Boardwalk room here. So much fun and different than usual rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Boardwalk Blast" by Escape Garden State in New York
review: Highly recommend Escape Garden State! Had so much fun in the Boardwalk Blast room with the family! Can't wait to go back for Power Surge!
